summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 4205, entitled "An Ordinance governing the traffic in intoxicating and malt liquors within the City of Seattle, and providing penalties for the violation thereof," approved June 2, 1896 and Ordinance No. 6413, approved December 4, 1900, Ordinance No. 8401, approved July 30, 1902 and Ordinance No. 9061, approved December 24, 1902, amendatory thereof.
